To apply the rules use this command inside mininet:


sh /home/sgsim/SmartGridSim/SGSIM_EXPERIMENTS/rules/zt_all_rules.sh

or one by one

sh /home/sgsim/SmartGridSim/SGSIM_EXPERIMENTS/rules/zt_dpsmv.sh
sh /home/sgsim/SmartGridSim/SGSIM_EXPERIMENTS/rules/zt_dpshv.sh
sh /home/sgsim/SmartGridSim/SGSIM_EXPERIMENTS/rules/zt_dpsrs.sh
sh /home/sgsim/SmartGridSim/SGSIM_EXPERIMENTS/rules/zt_dpsgw.sh

or 

sh /home/sgsim/SmartGridSim/SGSIM_EXPERIMENTS/rules/zt_dpsmv.sh; sh /home/sgsim/SmartGridSim/SGSIM_EXPERIMENTS/rules/zt_dpshv.sh; sh /home/sgsim/SmartGridSim/SGSIM_EXPERIMENTS/rules/zt_dpsrs.sh; sh /home/sgsim/SmartGridSim/SGSIM_EXPERIMENTS/rules/zt_dpsgw.sh

Start DOS attack inside mininet

mininet> ATTACKER sh -c "sleep 60; timeout 10s hping3 -S --flood -I ATTACKER-eth0 1.255.255.255"



